cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper is about sequential recommendation algorithms, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) applications. The proposed model involves attention mechanisms, which are also commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) tasks. Additionally, the model uses context information, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) applications.
